headline: INSTANT FREEPLAYS: CHIPOTLE TO REWARD FANS WITH FREE BURRITOS DURING THE 2025 MEN'S PROFESSIONAL BASKETBALL CHAMPIONSHIP SERIES
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced a new promotion called "Chipotle Instant Freeplays" ahead of the 2025 men's professional basketball championship series.
